Description: The CVriskMX package includes a set of functions to optimize cardiovascular risk 		prediction for Mexican adults. This package currently contains a function to estimate 		recalibrated risk for fatal cardiovascular disease using Globorisk (The Lancet Regional Health - Americas, 2026).
